    "title": "50+ SEO Prompts 2026: ChatGPT, Claude & Perplexity",
    "excerpt": "50+ copy-paste SEO prompts for AI-powered content optimization, technical audits, keyword research, and citation tracking. Free download.",
    "date": "Jul 2026",
