    "slug": "seo-portfolio-case-study",
    "title": "SEO Portfolio Case Study: Building Search and Citation Footprints from Scratch",
    "excerpt": "Review our detailed SEO and GEO case study. Learn the timeline, traffic growth patterns, AI citation wins, and key content lessons.",
    "date": "Feb 2026",
